detective and a forensic expert from Pretoria to assist the ICD in
their investigation," he said.
</P>
<P>
The ICD, an independent body which probes criminal allegations
against members of the South African Police Service, took over the
investigation on Sunday shortly after arriving at the scene.
</P>
<P>
The ANC in the KwaZulu-Natal province Monday morning called for
government assistance in the investigation, saying it is not
enough for the ICD to investigate. 
