<HEADLINE> Chinese Enterprises Meet Environmental Standards </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
QINGDAO, July 31 (Xinhua) -- All industrial enterprises in
China will meet national standards of waste disposal by the end of
the year, environmental official said here today.
</P>
<P>
