measures to control the discharge of waste on land to protect the
marine eco-system.
</P>
<P>
She noted that China has invested 25.1 billion yuan in
construction of 85 sewage treatment plants in 11 coastal provinces,
municipalities and autonomous regions over the past few years.
These plants have a total capacity of treating 12.27 million tons
of sewage from cities every day.
</P>
<P>
