environment is managed efficiently and that there are laws in
place which prevent "office pollution".
</P>
<P>
The bureau has already set strict rules on the control of 139
environmental problems in the office including water consumption,
electricity, paper waste, air quality and noise control. It also
banned spitting, random parking and smoking in public places.
