<HEADLINE> Indonesia Sets New Economic Reform Programs (Part 1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The signing of the memorandum is aimed at clearing the way for
the next 400 million U.S. dollars disbursement of loan package
from the Fund.
</P>
<P>
