<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Shanghai B Share Market Up at Monday Close </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 31 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai B share market index
rose 0.85 points, or 1.40 percent, to close at 61.78 Monday.
</P>
<P>
Turnover was 23.04 million U.S. dollars, which was 8.36 million
dollars, or 26.62 percent less than Friday's total, according to
information from Homeway, a leading online financial information
provider.
</P>
<P>
Buying increased as investors continue to dismiss profit
worries, and the index moved deeper into positive territory.
</P>
<P>
Gainers beat losers by 42 to 6, with seven unchanged. 
