<HEADLINE> Beijing to Host 5th Book Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Beijing will host the 5th Beijing
Book Fair from September 8 to 18, with 300 publishing houses
taking part.
</P>
<P>
Some 150,000 books, audio-visual products and electronic
publications will be up for sale during the Fair.
</P>
<P>
Different from previous book fairs, dozens of news publication
websites and book stores on-line will also attend.
</P>
