The Book Fair, sponsored by the Beijing municipal publicity
department and the Beijing press and publication bureau, will be
held in the Beijing Working People's Palace of Culture, the
Beijing Book Mansion, the Wangfujing Book Store, the China Book
Store and over 100 book stores throughout the city.
</P>
<P>
Statistics showed that more than 500,000 people attended the
Fourth Beijing Book Fair with 2.3 million copies of books sold
generating 20 million yuan. 
