<HEADLINE> China: Top of the Week (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
China will greatly increase the proportion of funds for social
security in budgetary expenditures, Minister of Finance Xiang
Huaicheng said in Beijing on July 25.
</P>
<P>
Xinhua, China's official news agency, on July 26 criticizes
Tsai Ying-wen, head of Taiwan's "Mainland Affairs Council," for
her separatist words and activities since she took office.
</P>
<P>
