<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 0030 GMT, July 31 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD -- Deposed Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif Sunday allowed
his Pakistan Muslim League (PML) to hold a "constructive and
meaningful dialogue" with the military government.
</P>
<P>
"I would welcome any constructive and meaningful dialogue with
the present regime. However, it has to be based on reciprocity and
