<HEADLINE> Toxic Spills in Brazil </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A communique said that the accident took place in the Osrio
pipeline in Paracambi, in the state of Rio de Janeiro, when the
MTBE, a substance added to oil, was being pumped.
</P>
<P>
Petrobras said that it has controlled the spill, and chances of
pollution are minimal.
</P>
