<HEADLINE> EU Provides Nicaragua 44 Mln Dls </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Nicaraguan Foreign Minister Eduardo Montealegre and chief of
the European Communities Commission Giorgio Mamberto signed the
agreements.
</P>
